name: Push Workout
description: A workout focused on pushing movements targeting chest, shoulders, and triceps.

exercises.name: Bench Press
exercises.description: Perform the bench press with a barbell or dumbbells to target the chest.

exercises.name: Overhead Press
exercises.description: Press the barbell or dumbbells overhead to target the shoulders.

exercises.name: Incline Dumbbell Press
exercises.description: Perform the press at an incline to focus on the upper chest.

exercises.name: Tricep Dips
exercises.description: Perform dips to target the triceps.

exercises.name: Lateral Raises
exercises.description: Raise the dumbbells to the side to target the lateral deltoids.
